      "rationale": "Eleven non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs were assembled from production-representative components and tested at two independent laboratories (n=6 and n=5). Statistical power analysis confirmed N=11 is sufficient to detect a 10% mean difference with 80% power at α=0.05. Required level 3 is met."
